snippet.title: Dance Nomads - KNOT : 놓을 수 없는 | 전국안무드래프트전 2023
snippet.description:
#현대무용 #contemporarydance #dancenomads
#전국안무드래프트전

Choreography by :
Kim Yoojung, Kathleen Carmelita

필사적으로 외면하고 싶었던 욕망, 끈질기게 나를 쫓아오는 욕구. 가질 수 없었기에 더욱 뜨거웠던 마음들을 애써 꾹꾹 누르고 나면, 그들은 기어코 나의 꿈에 그 모습을 드러내어 괴롭게 하곤 했다. 그런 밤이면 나는 욕구의 매듭에 목을 걸고, 절대 풀리지 않을 듯 단단한 매듭을 손가락으로 할퀴며 헐떡였다. 

내려놓는 것은 포기하는 것인가? 놓고 싶지 않은 사랑과 놓을 수 없는 춤. 풀 수 없다면 내려놓자고 다짐하는 밤들과, 숨막힐지언정 이 밧줄을 부여잡고 살겠노라 약속하는 날들.

snippet.title: KNOT:놓을 수 없는
My Graduation Performance 'Screen Time'  (but better quality)
snippet.description:
#graduation #contemporary #dancedepartment

A piece I choreographed myself for my graduation performance. This is my own story... I used to spend time alone in my room scrolling my phone only to see how people live their life. I could only see how happy and successful people were through the posts they made on social media. It made me insecure about my self. I felt that my life was far from perfect.
"I'm not as pretty as them", "I'm not as rich as them", "I'm not as talented as them", "I'm not as happy as them"
I kept comparing my self to others when I saw the posts on social media until I realized that what I did was just a waste of time and energy. 

People are special in their own way, and I am too! I stopped comparing my self to others and focused on what I can do. I worked hard to achieve what I wanted and that's when I got my confidence back!

snippet.description:
#billieeilish #burn #choreography

Piece description :
As an introvert, I find it hard for myself to be out there and communicate freely. Even I, myself, wish I could interact with people like an extrovert.
People say, "You can get better with practice!" "It’s just putting ourselves out there now and then." "Building relationship is important!" 
They meant good, but it's actually became a pressure for me to change.
Getting out of my own little space, doing things I'm not comfortable with...
I tried my best, but it's so draining.
Even after I get back to my own little space, I still feel the pressure to change, I can't love myself the way I am anymore.
I have to learn not only to understand myself, but accept and love myself
.
Created this solo months ago for a performance, when my left knee was still 'injury free'😒 Now my knee hurts just by watching it TT

snippet.title: I can't dance yet, so LET'S TALK! and do some TRE(?)
snippet.description:
#TRE #dance #letstalk

Hi guys! I just want to give a little update on how I'm doing now. I'm recovering faster than I expected, and hopefully, I'll be back with new dance videos starting next week!
Before that, through this video I just wanna share my thoughts and feelings, also something that has been helping me to go through difficult times. I've been doing TRE(Tension & Trauma Releasing Exercises) regularly for about a year now, it's been helping me to reduce my everyday's stress, and improve my  health too.
Moreover, it's been helping me to recover from the injuries I suffered from the accident too. If you're interested in this exercise and want to find out more about it, you can check out the website here...
https://traumaprevention.com/what-is-tre/
